_sText: This map has buyzones, so that it can be played as a gungame map, or as an aim/fy map. About This Map I was rather inspired when I saw someone's dev textured version of their map ( http://farm1.static.flickr.com/186/394525257_fc10adc481.jpg ). I liked it a lot, so I copied the idea. Then I took the curve idea maps like gg_circular. When I first created this map, I didn't think it would work out at all. It works much better than I imagined! The blue color from my custom textures comes from the Tango Project icon palette.
